Changelog:
----------

2009-07-25 v1.0.1 by Maurice Makaay

   - Fixed a little bug that caused the login check to fail.

   - After logging in, the browser was sent back to the "you need to login"
     page. Now, the user that logged in will be redirected to the
     profile page that the user was originally visiting.

   - Implemented language support for the module.

   - Added a README and Changelog.

2009-07-25 v1.0.0 by Ravenswood

   - Initial release

